## 🚀 安装方式

### 方式 1：从 Monorepo 安装

```bash
git clone https://github.com/fclwtt/openclaw-tt.git
cd openclaw-tt/{{SKILL_NAME}}
./install.sh
```

### 方式 2：ClawHub 安装

```bash
clawhub install {{SKILL_NAME}}
```

### 方式 3：OpenClaw 命令

```bash
openclaw skills install {{SKILL_NAME}}
```

